com.phunware.location

Class PwLocationUpdateResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.phunware.location.PwLocationUpdateResult

  • public class PwLocationUpdateResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains all possible error codes for when a client fails to connect to PwLocationProvider. These error codes are used by PwLocationListener.onLocationUpdateFailed(PwLocationUpdateResult).
    See Also:
    ConnectionResult
